# Environment Variables

## Development

```bash
# Backend API endpoint
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
```

## Production

```bash
# Backend API endpoint (update with your production URL)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.com
```

## Notes

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix makes variables available in the browser
- Keep sensitive keys in `.env.local` (git-ignored)
- Auth tokens are stored in localStorage (secure over HTTPS only)
